@@ -1,20 +1,32 @@
 /** @file
-  Find and extract QEMU SMBIOS data from fw_cfg.
+Find and extract QEMU SMBIOS data from fw_cfg.
 
+  This file has been modified to disable SMBIOS table loading from QEMU
+  in order to bypass Virtual Machine detection mechanisms.
